---
import Footer from "./components/Footer.astro";
import Head from "./components/Head.astro";
import Navigation from "./components/Navigation.astro";
---
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <Head />
        <title>Privacy Policy - Ruthless To Do List</title>
    </head>
    <body class="bg-light-1 text-dark-5">
        <Navigation />
        <div class="grid gap-4 p-6 text-xl md:p-10">
            <h1 class="text-5xl">Privacy Policy for Ruthless To Do List</h1>
            <p class="text-dark-3">Last Updated: April 16, 2024</p>

            <p>Welcome to Ruthless To Do List! We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we handle your personal information when you use our app.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl">1. No Data Collection</h2>
            <p>We want you to know that Ruthless To Do List does not collect any personal data or information from its users in any way. We believe in privacy by design, and our app is designed to function without needing to collect or store any user data.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl">2. Usage Data</h2>
            <p>While the app may generate some usage data for improving user experience and performance, this data is strictly anonymous and cannot be used to identify individual users. This includes information such as the number of times the app is opened, feature usage, and app crashes. This data is solely used for internal purposes to enhance the app's functionality and performance.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>Ruthless To Do List does not integrate with any third-party services that would require access to your personal information or data. We do not share any user data with third parties.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl">4. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last Updated" date. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl">5. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at:</p>

            <p>Email: <a class="underline text-main" href="mailto:ruthlesstodolist@czino.de">ruthlesstodolist@czino.de</a></p>
        </div>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
